data.description: Welcome to your perfect home on the prairie side of charming Colorado Springs! This 4-bed, 3-bath beauty sits on the southeast corner, offering breathtaking mountain views just a glance away.    Step inside to 2544 sqft of pure comfort. The main level is your cozy haven, featuring 2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, including a master suite fit for relaxation royalty. No stairs? No problem! Enjoy the ease of main-level living with every essential right at your fingertips.    The heart of the home is a dreamy kitchen, perfect for whipping up family feasts or hosting friends. The three-car garage ensures plenty of space for vehicles, hobbies, or that collection of adventure gear you've been eyeing.    Venture downstairs to the vast basement, a playground for possibilities. Two extra bedrooms and a full bathroom await your personal touch—create the ultimate guest suite, home gym, or entertainment hub. The choice is yours!    As you unwind in the open space behind the house, let nature serenade you. While the mountain views aren't knocking on your front door, they're just a gaze away, providing a picturesque backdrop to your prairie paradise.     filled with endless potential,  is more than a home; it's an invitation to a lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to make this slice of Colorado Springs yours!
